{"tid":810443,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"（侵侵大敗)【貿易戰】美國上月貿易逆差急升10%！2015年以來最多","createTime":"2018-09-08T03:49:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T04:52:10.000Z","uid":147097,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2fefaa929afaf46e9e2c5c3676024f59d3d60918","tid":810443,"uid":147097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T03:49:31.000Z","msg":"美國7月貿易逆差由6月457億美元，急升9.5%至501億美元，幅度達10%，為2015年以最大升幅。是次急升主要是因為大豆及民營飛機出口下跌所致，與此同時入口貿易數量達到紀錄新高所致，或有機會影響第3季經濟表現。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">單單是對中國貿易逆差，亦升10%至368億美元。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7b0091e87a4ace071c336759a1a6a3e8de4a949","tid":810443,"uid":119502,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T03:50:46.000Z","msg":"Ching快d走，侵粉黎緊啦"},{"pid":"1e77b06aa4d35285e22e2270fef8e153648db641","tid":810443,"uid":89225,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T04:03:45.000Z","msg":"星期一夾番五舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d690e4bb48e71c42805a3cb9ed1af03980b9595","tid":810443,"uid":56698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T04:04:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6ab62d108cb8263967a801f8eaf89ef8d46402f","tid":810443,"uid":58413,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T04:06:25.000Z","msg":"係咪正常？有巴打提過要再加稅前盡出單先，連聖誕果水貨都鬥快出緊，之後就仆街囉。 <br />\n<br />\n如果唔係,咁侵侵要加多d囉。"},{"pid":"8524d7ab69ece076baa53179236d5c4bd2bcd04d","tid":810443,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T04:13:50.000Z","msg":"牛3啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db0df9e201f951140458a569b8f82ec592b096b9","tid":810443,"uid":31186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T04:20:16.000Z","msg":"贏國又贏"},{"pid":"b2b4b03b07ca8f3f177e5e0e5f0e0ee547bdca90","tid":810443,"u